title: Whelchel completes second ironman triathlon (Henderson State University)
text: ( Source : Henderson State University ) Penny Whelchel, assistant professor of family and consumer sciences and director of dietetics specialization at Henderson State , completed her second Ironman Triathlon Oct. 17 in Wilmington, N.C. ,
